data.description: Welcome to this inviting solid brick ranch home in a convenient NW Location. Great curb appeal.  Discover the warmth of hardwood flooring on the main floor.  Charming kitchen with knotty pine wood. Connected to the home is a breezeway for enjoying that's leads to the garage. Full basement where you will even more living space to enjoy, a cozy family room, a bar area beckons for socializing and creating lasting memories, stools are included.  Also features a bathroom, along with plenty of storage stage to accomodate your needs.  Step outside to the fenced backyard where you,  your pets, friends, children and unwind and enjoy outdoor activities including a fire pit area.
